The aim of this project is to determine a suitable time to use the public transportation around the popular tourist area in NY by the consumers of RTA company. At this stage of the project,Empire State Building, Central Park and Times Square were chosen to conduct the data analysis.
Several methods of data cleaning were applied to prepare the data. Then, specific stations were selected based on the direction to Empire State Building, Central Park and Times Square. For example, these transit lines [‘Hudson’, ‘Long Beach’, ‘Montauk’, ‘Path’, ‘Port Washington’] have routes that pass near Empire State Building
